    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Papaya</h1>
    <hr>
    <figure>
        <img src="https://github.com/sumayamohammad/Lab-4/blob/c8d935fc11e2957a931bd17bf8a7823f4a283cd8/Images/intro-1684865402.jpg" 
